{"tid":2371551,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[We can face all HKers]狗賊：邊個影相就咬邊個","createTime":"2021-01-19T03:23:57.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-19T05:29:05.000Z","uid":51271,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"10c9023a66dbad74137ff6401c62c76315d42cc1","tid":2371551,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T03:23:57.000Z","msg":"高級督察作供   疑似警護送阻影相    威嚇「邊個影相拉邊個」<br />\n<br />\n2019年 8 月 10 日紅磡非法集結、管有爆炸品等案，案件今（ 18 日）於區域法院續審，高級督察陳曉馳今早完成作供後，由數名疑似警員護送，經灣仔政府大樓UB停車場範圍離開，而該停車場範圍並不屬於法院範圍，傳媒過往一直可於該處拍照採訪，惟是次傳媒拍攝期間，數名疑似警員阻礙拍攝，更有人一度表示，「邊個影相拉邊個」，記者澄清該處可拍攝後，對方仍不罷休，並指「點解我唔可以遮住你個鏡頭呀？」及他有肖像權等，記者出示記者證後，對方又表示，「立場呀...你係咪正式傳媒機構呢？」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://fb.watch/362BrHL-DA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffb.watch%2F362BrHL-DA%2F&d=aWm579aYkHvvwdD7ZyOwrIgmK84TLJm0fByd7TIP4s4%3D&h=4e891da9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://fb.watch/362BrHL-DA/</a>"},{"pid":"a017defc9568f8403b0713d00ff0dae5094171e0","tid":2371551,"uid":251732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T03:25:27.000Z","msg":"你哋呢班仆街仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afcfcb83bd816cc30cff59c879a9d42e6216cda3","tid":2371551,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T03:25:54.000Z","msg":"好大嘅狗威"},{"pid":"828fb3624140442a550904c7a72fde7df9eee6ed","tid":2371551,"uid":7369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T03:27:03.000Z","msg":"肖像權<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1158d60144095b40ce1802221d4e0db2052937c6","tid":2371551,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"828fb3624140442a550904c7a72fde7df9eee6ed","tid":2371551,"uid":7369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T03:27:03.000Z","msg":"肖像權<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T03:27:29.000Z","msg":"支那就有<img src